00:01:25.779 --> 00:01:28.220
And he says, how say ye to my soul,

00:01:28.220 --> 00:01:29.900
flee as a bird to your mountain.

00:01:29.900 --> 00:01:32.900
And I mentioned as we studied that portion of scripture

00:01:32.900 --> 00:01:35.500
that we need to be careful who we listen to,

00:01:35.500 --> 00:01:38.260
