00:07:39.700 --> 00:07:41.940
We find that this principle understood,

00:07:41.940 --> 00:07:45.140
I'll make two thoughts with regard to the principle,

00:07:45.140 --> 00:07:46.779
share some verses of scripture,

00:07:46.779 --> 00:07:49.980
