00:08:02.500 --> 00:08:04.940
And I'm so thankful that God is my rock.

00:08:05.679 --> 00:08:07.799
He is my defense, he's my fortress.

00:08:07.799 --> 00:08:09.239
I'm thankful this evening,

00:08:09.239 --> 00:08:11.119
when we talk about the Lord, he's my shield,

00:08:11.119 --> 00:08:14.760
he's a strong tower, I'm thankful for the defense.

00:08:14.760 --> 00:08:18.600
The Bible speaks about safety is of the Lord.

00:08:18.600 --> 00:08:20.720
And what a blessing to understand

00:08:20.720 --> 00:08:23.160
that though David was in this situation,

00:08:23.160 --> 00:08:25.600
and though the wicked had bent their bow,

00:08:25.600 --> 00:08:27.679
