00:10:00.000 --> 00:10:01.279
we could understand it.

00:10:01.279 --> 00:10:03.079
He says, this is the condemnation

00:10:03.079 --> 00:10:04.320
that light is coming to the world

00:10:04.320 --> 00:10:06.440
and men love darkness rather than light.

00:10:06.440 --> 00:10:07.280
Why?

00:10:07.280 --> 00:10:08.720
